Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:06.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错恋离散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮料还没给上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:11.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨み節さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:11.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨漫漫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所点的饮料  给您拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.22,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠いあんたにゃ届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.22,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远方之君　无计达意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.76,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佇んで泣き…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伫立于风　以泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等一下  那个茶色的是我的啦
