Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十路岬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈——真爽啊
